CEA2D

Class Population

  • java.lang.Object
    • CEA2D.Population

  • public class Population
extends java.lang.Object
    The class population represents the whole population for the evolutionary algorithm SSEA2D. It contains all the representations and the function to evolve a new generation.
    Author:
    Thomas Dittrich
